org.openhubframework.openhub.core.config.datasource

Annotation Type OpenHubDataSource


  • @Target(value={CONSTRUCTOR,FIELD,METHOD,ANNOTATION_TYPE,PARAMETER})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Autowired
 @Qualifier(value="OpenHubDataSource")
public @interface OpenHubDataSource
    Alias for Resource annotation to autowire bean with "OpenHubDataSource" name. Note that we cannot use Autowired with Qualifier, as if only one DataSource is does not inject by bean name.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Tomas Hanus

    • Field Detail

      • BEAN_NAME

        public static final String BEAN_NAME
        Bean name of DataSource.
